window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Mason will soon leave Nalnora, but he’s going out with a bang.</p> <p>As the Master continues to topple and possess the weaker elven Houses, Mason decides to up their offense. Guns might be deadly...but a bazooka decimates.</p> <p>Especially one powered by runes.</p> <p>So, with the help of his few elven allies, Mason works to loosen the Master’s grip on Nalnora one last time.</p> <p>The Master’s army marches for war, but Mason is ready for them.</p>"; 
